## API Routes

All under `/api/`. JWT-protected unless noted.

- `GET /health` ‚Äî health check (no auth)
- `GET /time` ‚Äî server UTC time (no auth)
- `GET /ws` ‚Äî WebSocket (token via query param)
- `/auth/*` ‚Äî register, login, refresh, logout
- `/users/*` ‚Äî CRUD, roles, permissions, suspension
- `/forum/*` ‚Äî categories, threads, comments, likes
- `/store/*` ‚Äî products, cart, checkout, orders, subscriptions
- `/inbox/*` ‚Äî conversations, messages, unread count
- `/notifications/*` ‚Äî list, read, delete
- `/config/*` ‚Äî branding, SEO, footer, features, landing, pages
- `/upload/*` ‚Äî image, video, file, banner

## Security Checklist

- bcrypt cost 12 for passwords
- HS256 JWT with env-sourced secret
- CORS explicit origin allowlist (no wildcards)
- Rate limiting per IP
- RBAC on all protected endpoints
- MIME type allowlist for uploads
- Path traversal guards on file serving
- Token redaction in logs
- `Cache-Control: no-store` on API responses
- Non-root container user (`appuser`)
- Configurable DB connection pool limits
